dct_title_s: Map of the famous 101 mile drive on the Rim of the World
dct_alternative_sm: Map of the famous 101 mile drive on the Rim of the World, San Bernardino Mountains California Showing resorts, lakes and fishing streams
dct_description_sm: Automobile Club of Southern California ; A.J.B.
Relief shown by hachures and spot heights.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows city plans, roads, railroads, waterways, power houses, resorts.
Belongs to a series of maps showing roads in California.
